         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Pakteutes, son of Ereson son of Gorsenuphis for the merismos of the 7th year of lord Hadrian:  4 drachmas, totals 4 drachmas.  Year 7; 1st of Phaophi. The 8th of Hathyr, for the merismos, 4 drachmas, totals 4 drachmas.</ab>
